Updating financial disclosure (where previous disclosure has been by Form E1)

(typically cases under children act 1989, schedule 1)

Each party shall by [time and date] / [[time] on the date [number] weeks prior to the [financial dispute resolution appointment] / [final hearing] / [insert] listed at [para number] below] serve on the other party a schedule of the following financial disclosure (with statements and/or documents attached) updated since the last disclosure provided and which shall include any which have been opened or otherwise come into existence since financial disclosure was last provided:

mortgages;

bank and building society accounts;

investments;

policies;

liabilities;

business/trading accounts;

the Cash Equivalent of pension rights (or value of any PPF rights);

P60s and P11Ds;

